cess sites:\n    - `createJmDnsVersion1`\n    - `buildServiceInfoVersion1`\n  - Handles Native Image’s unsupported dynamic class loading path using `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per workflow instructions.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02a07c3e861287e7016a25f70c1b188194b15888ad9938f6c0\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 313, "output": 1317, "cacheRead": 56832, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 58462, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780872945640, "responseId": "resp_02a07c3e861287e7016a25f6f2a3c881948caf55316e420d04"}, "toolResults": []}
