Invokes the public `advertise(...)` / `unadvertise(...)` flow to reach:\n    - `buildServiceInfoVersion1(...)`\n    - legacy `registerService(...)`\n    - legacy `unregisterService(...)`\n  - Invokes the private static legacy initialization helper only to reach `createJmDnsVersion1(...)`, since that call site is otherwise only reachable during class static initialization with a v1 JmDNS classpath.\n\n- Simplified `build.gradle`\n  - Removed the unused `oldJmDns` configuration and native/JVM system property wiring.\n  - Kept `org.jmdns:jmdns:3.5.7` for the normal supported v3 path.\n\nFiles changed:\n\n- `tests/src/org.apache.logging.log4j/log4j-core/2.17.1/build.gradle`\n- `tests/src/org.apache.logging.log4j/log4j-core/2.17.1/src/test/java/org_apache_logging_log4j/log4j_core/MulticastDnsAdvertiserTest.java`\n\nI did not run tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02a07c3e861287e7016a25fa8657408194b6440f4c94d931c7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 480, "output": 1101, "cacheRead": 77824, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 79405, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780873842728, "responseId": "resp_02a07c3e861287e7016a25fa73ea388194b754fba7dcd3da51"}, "toolResults": []}
